# Q4 — DOW Mission Reports grouped by Combatant Command (COCOM).
# The `mission` relation is the top-level hierarchical hyperedge from
# entry 04. COCOM is one of its role-typed participants. Expected:
# 23 USCENTCOM, 1 USEUCOM, 1 redacted (the COCOM itself was [1.4a]).

match
  $m  isa mission, links (cocom-unit: $cc);
  $cc has name $n;
reduce $c = count groupby $n;
